Name: eventType
Description:
-obtained header of the SUBSCRIBE
1 = Registration
2 = Presence
3 = Conference
4 = Dialog
5 = Call-info

Name: subscriptionResult
Description:
-1 = Event subscription message not available
0 = Success (when 200 OK received is followed by NOTIFY, and applies to all Event Types)
1 = Failure (when any error other than 401 is received; else when 408 timeout occurs)
